{"tid":1479939,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國金融核武=拋美債？下，點拋呀？","createTime":"2019-08-17T05:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T18:02:20.000Z","uid":20948,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5509a031e3377abc55f303f13a28c0ba8f844baa","tid":1479939,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:56:14.000Z","msg":"其實中國好多美債都已經到期，但中國有冇叫美國還錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解冇？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為買返黎啲美債全部抵押去銀行，換返美金，作為外匯儲備<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n即係中國要拋美債首先要贖回美債<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁你估下邊個息口高？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n要拋美債換錢隨時要先付出更大成本<br />\n<br />\n就算退一萬步當中國想攬炒，<span style=\"color: green;\">你覺得中國而家有冇錢啟動攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好驕都唔好灰，而家正值中國內憂外患，堅持就有曙光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49b363c9a55b0cbacf61e85b8b33dcb03e6de80","tid":1479939,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7090866383a3cfe81106f97a49a6a20899ebf6b","tid":1479939,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i